---
title: Tofu Bulgogi-Style Bowls with Buttered Rice, Corn and Gochujang Mayo
description: Buttered corn and rice serve as the base for delicious, savoury flavours in this family-friendly tofu dish! A dollop of gochujang mayo—for those who can handle a little spice—adds the perfect amount of sweet heat to every bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-boeuf-et-de-porc-facon-bulgogi-0955db6d-119585b0.jpg
